---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="CA Accounting | Los Angeles CPA & Tax Firm"
  description="An AICPA-member Los Angeles accounting firm headquartered in Glendale. Led by a CPA and an Enrolled Agent. Tax, accounting, and advisory services for businesses and individuals throughout California."
>
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="bg-cream-warm relative overflow-hidden">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 grid-bg opacity-60"></div>
    <div class="container-custom py-20 md:py-28 relative">
      <div class="max-w-4xl">
        <p class="text-forest font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-6 fade-in">
          Los Angeles · Glendale-Based · Over 20 Years
        </p>
        <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-6xl lg:text-7xl font-serif text-navy leading-[1.05] mb-8 fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
          A Los Angeles CPA firm with <em class="font-normal italic">over twenty years</em> of experience.
        </h1>
        <p class="text-charcoal text-lg md:text-xl leading-relaxed max-w-2xl mb-10 fade-in fade-in-delay-2">
          An AICPA-member firm led by a Certified Public Accountant and an Enrolled Agent. Tax, accounting, and advisory services for businesses and individuals throughout California.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 fade-in fade-in-delay-3">
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="btn-modern bg-forest text-cream font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded text-center hover:bg-forest-hover"
          >
            Schedule a Free Consultation
          </a>
          <a
            href="tel:8775009290"
            class="btn-modern border border-navy text-navy font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded text-center hover:bg-navy hover:text-cream"
          >
            Call 877.500.9290
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- What we do -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mb-16 fade-in">
        <p class="text-forest font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">What We Do</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-serif text-navy mb-6">
          Three areas of practice.<br />One unified team.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-lg leading-relaxed">
          Whether you need year-round tax planning, dependable bookkeeping, or strategic financial leadership, we provide the full range of services a growing business needs from its accounting partner.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <div class="card-elevated bg-white rounded-xl p-8 fade-in">
          <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between mb-6">
            <span class="editorial-number text-3xl">01</span>
            <div class="w-8 h-px bg-forest"></div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif text-navy mb-4">Tax Services</h3>
          <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-base leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Year-round tax planning, return preparation, IRS audit assistance, and estate and retirement planning, led by an Enrolled Agent.
          </p>
          <a href="/services#tax" class="link-underline text-forest font-semibold text-sm">
            Tax services →
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="card-elevated bg-white rounded-xl p-8 fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
          <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between mb-6">
            <span class="editorial-number text-3xl">02</span>
            <div class="w-8 h-px bg-forest"></div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif text-navy mb-4">Accounting & Bookkeeping</h3>
          <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-base leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Outsourced bookkeeping, payroll, financial statement preparation, and reviews for owners who would rather run the business than the back office.
          </p>
          <a href="/services#accounting" class="link-underline text-forest font-semibold text-sm">
            Accounting services →
          </a>
        </div>

        <div class="card-elevated bg-white rounded-xl p-8 fade-in fade-in-delay-2">
          <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between mb-6">
            <span class="editorial-number text-3xl">03</span>
            <div class="w-8 h-px bg-forest"></div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif text-navy mb-4">Outsourced CFO & Controller</h3>
          <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-base leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Cash flow management, financial reporting, audits, business valuation, and M&A support for businesses that need senior financial leadership.
          </p>
          <a href="/services#cfo" class="link-underline text-forest font-semibold text-sm">
            CFO services →
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Industries we know -->
  <section class="bg-navy text-cream py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mb-16 fade-in">
        <p class="text-cream/60 font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Areas of Expertise</p>
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-serif text-cream mb-6">
          Industry depth where it matters.
        </h2>
        <p class="text-cream/80 text-lg leading-relaxed">
          CA Accounting works with businesses in a variety of industries throughout California. We have particular depth in three: entertainment, medical practices, and real estate.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-6">
        <a href="/industries/entertainment" class="group bg-navy-deep border border-cream/10 rounded-xl p-8 hover:border-cream/30 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 fade-in">
          <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between mb-6">
            <span class="editorial-number text-3xl text-cream/40">01</span>
            <div class="w-8 h-px bg-cream/20 group-hover:bg-cream/60 transition-colors"></div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif text-cream mb-4">Entertainment</h3>
          <p class="text-cream/70 text-base leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Actors, singers, songwriters and athletes can minimize their tax burden and increase profits with our accounting and tax solutions.
          </p>
          <span class="link-underline text-cream/90 font-semibold text-sm">Learn more →</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/industries/medical" class="group bg-navy-deep border border-cream/10 rounded-xl p-8 hover:border-cream/30 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
          <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between mb-6">
            <span class="editorial-number text-3xl text-cream/40">02</span>
            <div class="w-8 h-px bg-cream/20 group-hover:bg-cream/60 transition-colors"></div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif text-cream mb-4">Medical Practices</h3>
          <p class="text-cream/70 text-base leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Doctors, dentists, chiropractors, veterinarians and other medical practitioners benefit from our combination of practice management, bookkeeping, and tax strategies.
          </p>
          <span class="link-underline text-cream/90 font-semibold text-sm">Learn more →</span>
        </a>

        <a href="/industries/real-estate" class="group bg-navy-deep border border-cream/10 rounded-xl p-8 hover:border-cream/30 hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 fade-in fade-in-delay-2">
          <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between mb-6">
            <span class="editorial-number text-3xl text-cream/40">03</span>
            <div class="w-8 h-px bg-cream/20 group-hover:bg-cream/60 transition-colors"></div>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-serif text-cream mb-4">Real Estate</h3>
          <p class="text-cream/70 text-base leading-relaxed mb-6">
            Property managers, developers, investors, brokers and agents save time with outsourced accounting and avoid tax problems with our planning strategies.
          </p>
          <span class="link-underline text-cream/90 font-semibold text-sm">Learn more →</span>
        </a>
      </div>

      <p class="text-cream/70 text-center text-sm mt-12 fade-in">
        Don't see your industry? <a href="/industries" class="link-underline text-cream font-semibold">CA Accounting works with businesses across many sectors throughout California →</a>
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Why firms hire us -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="fade-in">
          <p class="text-forest font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-4">Why Clients Stay</p>
          <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-serif text-navy mb-6">
            An AICPA-member firm.
          </h2>
          <p class="text-charcoal text-lg leading-relaxed mb-6">
            CA Accounting is a member firm of the American Institute of Certified Public Accountants. Our partners hold the credentials at the center of the profession: a Certified Public Accountant and an Enrolled Agent.
          </p>
          <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-base leading-relaxed">
            Over 20 years of experience. Many of our client relationships measure in decades.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-px bg-line border border-line rounded-xl overflow-hidden fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
          <div class="bg-cream p-8">
            <div class="text-5xl font-serif text-navy mb-2">20+</div>
            <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">Years of practice</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-cream p-8">
            <div class="text-5xl font-serif text-navy mb-2">AICPA</div>
            <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">Member firm</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-cream p-8">
            <div class="text-5xl font-serif text-navy mb-2">CPA</div>
            <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">Managing Partner</p>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-cream p-8">
            <div class="text-5xl font-serif text-navy mb-2">EA</div>
            <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm uppercase tracking-wider">Founding Partner</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Featured testimonial -->
  <section class="bg-cream-warm py-20 md:py-28">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto fade-in relative">
        <p class="text-forest font-semibold text-sm uppercase tracking-widest mb-8 text-center">In Our Clients' Words</p>
        <div class="text-forest/30 font-serif text-9xl leading-none mb-[-2rem] text-center select-none" aria-hidden="true">"</div>
        <blockquote class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-serif text-navy leading-snug mb-10 text-center">
          It's always a pleasure working with Rima, Narek and Farshid at CA Accounting. They're not only wonderful people but also exceptionally talented, precise, and driven in their work. I've worked with them across two different companies now and can confidently recommend them to anyone looking for reliable accounting and finance support.
        </blockquote>
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-12 h-px bg-forest mx-auto mb-4"></div>
          <p class="text-charcoal font-semibold">J. Sider</p>
          <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-sm">Google Review · ★★★★★</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Other testimonials -->
  <section class="py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
        <div class="border-l-2 border-forest pl-6 fade-in">
          <p class="text-charcoal text-base leading-relaxed mb-4 italic">
            "The accounting team is trustworthy and reliable. They make it easy to work with and are great partners for entrepreneurs like me."
          </p>
          <p class="text-charcoal font-semibold text-sm">Melva Benoit</p>
          <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-xs">The Marian Dupree Group</p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-l-2 border-forest pl-6 fade-in fade-in-delay-1">
          <p class="text-charcoal text-base leading-relaxed mb-4 italic">
            "Couldn't be happier with the service at CA Accounting. Farshid, Lucy and the whole team. Very attentive to details and most important... Knowledgeable! I highly recommend them."
          </p>
          <p class="text-charcoal font-semibold text-sm">Ernie Fregozo</p>
          <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-xs">Google Local Guide</p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-l-2 border-forest pl-6 fade-in fade-in-delay-2">
          <p class="text-charcoal text-base leading-relaxed mb-4 italic">
            "Farshid and all his team have been instrumental in strengthening our financial understanding."
          </p>
          <p class="text-charcoal font-semibold text-sm">Dave Mason</p>
          <p class="text-charcoal-muted text-xs">Rock and Roll Hall of Fame inductee</p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="text-center mt-12 fade-in">
        <a href="/testimonials" class="link-underline text-forest font-semibold text-sm">Read more client stories →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Final CTA -->
  <section class="bg-navy text-cream py-20 md:py-24">
    <div class="container-custom">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto text-center fade-in">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-serif text-cream mb-6">
          Ready to talk?
        </h2>
        <p class="text-cream/80 text-lg leading-relaxed mb-10">
          The first conversation is free. Schedule a consultation and we will tell you how we can help.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a
            href="/contact"
            class="btn-modern bg-forest text-cream font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded hover:bg-forest-hover"
          >
            Schedule a Free Consultation
          </a>
          <a
            href="tel:8775009290"
            class="btn-modern border border-cream/40 text-cream font-semibold px-8 py-4 rounded hover:bg-cream/10"
          >
            Call 877.500.9290
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
